        Mean(list)

*PARMS

{list} -- list of values

*DESC

This function calculates the mean of a list of values.

*E.G.
In> Mean([73,94,80,37,56,94,40,21,7,24])
Result: 263/5

In> NM(Mean([73,94,80,37,56,94,40,21,7,24]))
